                <note rend="inline" type="source">811.20(D)Regulations/3305: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in Iran</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dreyfus</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1941-07-24T20:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 24, 1941—8 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>59. Your 72, July 14, 10 a.m. Application of June 10 was rejected July 21 but
                    United States Steel Export Corporation has now been invited to submit new
                    application which will be considered in connection with Prime Minister’s
                    recommendation.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Welles</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
